        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                    <p><img src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/Screenshot_36.png" class="type:primaryImage" alt="" /></p>
                <p>O Oh My Posh é uma ferramenta poderosa para personalizar e melhorar a experiência do PowerShell no Windows 11. Neste tutorial, vamos orientar passo a passo como instalar e configurar o Oh My Posh para transformar o seu prompt do PowerShell em algo mais dinâmico e estilizado.</p>
<h2>1. Instalação do PowerShell</h2>
<p>Para começar, certifique-se de que o PowerShell está instalado em seu sistema. No Windows 11, o PowerShell normalmente já vem pré-instalado. Caso não tenha, você pode instalá-lo através da Microsoft Store ou pelo pacote de instalação disponível no site oficial da Microsoft.</p>
<div class="gallery-wrapper"><div class="gallery"  data-is-empty="false" data-translation="Adicione imagens" data-columns="8">
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_1-2.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_1-2-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_2-2.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_2-2-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_3-2.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_3-2-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_4-2.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_4-2-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
</div></div>
<h2>2. Instalação do Oh My Posh via winget</h2>
<p>O Oh My Posh pode ser instalado usando o winget, o novo gerenciador de pacotes do Windows. Execute o seguinte comando no PowerShell:</p>
<div class="bg-black rounded-md">
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">winget install JanDeDobbeleer.OhMyPosh -s winget
</code></div>
</div>
<div class="gallery-wrapper"><div class="gallery"  data-is-empty="false" data-translation="Adicione imagens" data-columns="8">
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_9.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_9-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_8.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_8-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
</div></div>
<h2>3. Configuração das fontes do Oh My Posh</h2>
<p>Para configurar as fontes do Oh My Posh, utilize o seguinte comando:</p>
<div class="bg-black rounded-md">
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">oh-my-posh font install
</code></div>
</div>
<div class="gallery-wrapper"><div class="gallery"  data-is-empty="false" data-translation="Adicione imagens" data-columns="8">
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_10.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_10-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_11.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_11-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_12.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_12-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_17.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_17-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_18.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_18-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
</div></div>
<h2>4. Configurando o Prompt do Oh My Posh</h2>
<p>Crie um novo perfil do PowerShell, se não existir, e inicialize o Oh My Posh nele:</p>
<div class="bg-black rounded-md">
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">New-Item -Path $PROFILE -Type File -Force<br>oh-my-posh init pwsh | Invoke-Expression
</code></div>
</div>
<div class="gallery-wrapper"><div class="gallery"  data-is-empty="false" data-translation="Adicione imagens" data-columns="8">
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_13.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_13-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_14.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_14-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_15.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_15-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_19.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_19-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
</div></div>
<h2>5. Escolher o Tema do seu Oh My Posh</h2>
<p>Você pode escolher um tema para o Oh My Posh de acordo com suas preferências:</p>
<div class="bg-black rounded-md">
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">Get-PoshThemes</code></div>
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">oh-my-posh init pwsh --config 'C:\Users\SeuUsuario\AppData\Local\Programs\oh-my-posh\themes\negligible.omp.json' | Invoke-Expression
</code></div>
</div>
<p><em>Lembre-se de substituir "SeuUsuario" pelo seu nome de usuário no Windows.</em></p>
<div class="gallery-wrapper"><div class="gallery"  data-is-empty="false" data-translation="Adicione imagens" data-columns="8">
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_20.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_20-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_21.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_21-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_22.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_22-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_23.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_23-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_24.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_24-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
</div></div>
<h2>6. Instalar e configurar o Terminal-Icons</h2>
<p>Adicione e configure os ícones no terminal com os seguintes comandos:</p>
<div class="bg-black rounded-md">
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">Install-Module -Name Terminal-Icons -Repository PSGallery</code><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell"></code></div>
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">Import-Module -Name Terminal-Icons
</code></div>
</div>
<div class="gallery-wrapper"><div class="gallery"  data-is-empty="false" data-translation="Adicione imagens" data-columns="8">
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_25.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_25-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_26.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_26-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_27.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_27-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_28.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_28-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_29.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_29-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
</div></div>
<h2>7. Instalar e configurar o Git-Posh</h2>
<p>Para integrar o Git ao seu prompt, instale e configure o Git-Posh:</p>
<div class="bg-black rounded-md">
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">PowerShellGet\Install-Module posh-git -Scope CurrentUser -Force</code></div>
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">Import-Module posh-git
</code></div>
</div>
<h2>8. Instalar e Configurar o PSReadLine</h2>
<p>Aprimore sua experiência no PowerShell instalando e configurando o PSReadLine:</p>
<div class="bg-black rounded-md">
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">Install-Module PSReadLine -AllowPrerelease -Force</code></div>
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">Import-Module PSReadLine</code></div>
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">Set-PSReadLineOption -PredictionSource History</code></div>
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">Set-PSReadLineOption -PredictionViewStyle ListView</code></div>
<div class="p-4 overflow-y-auto"><code class="!whitespace-pre hljs language-powershell">Set-PSReadLineOption -EditMode Windows
</code></div>
</div>
<div class="gallery-wrapper"><div class="gallery"  data-is-empty="false" data-translation="Adicione imagens" data-columns="8">
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_30.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_30-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_33.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_33-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_32.png" data-size="1919x1079"><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/gallery/Screenshot_32-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a></figure>
</div></div>
<h2>Conclusão</h2>
<p>Ao seguir estes passos, você configurou com sucesso o Oh My Posh no seu PowerShell do Windows 11. Personalize-o ainda mais explorando diferentes temas, fontes e configurações disponíveis para criar um ambiente que se adeque ao seu estilo de trabalho e preferências.</p>
<figure class="post__image" ><img loading="lazy" src="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/Screenshot_35-2.png" alt="" width="1919" height="1079" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/responsive/Screenshot_35-2-xs.png 300w ,https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/responsive/Screenshot_35-2-sm.png 480w ,https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/responsive/Screenshot_35-2-md.png 768w ,https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/responsive/Screenshot_35-2-lg.png 1024w ,https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/responsive/Screenshot_35-2-xl.png 1360w ,https://alesonmedeiros.com.br/media/posts/3/responsive/Screenshot_35-2-2xl.png 1600w">
<figcaption >Meu arquivo $PROFILE</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>Lembre-se sempre de consultar a documentação oficial do Oh My Posh para obter informações adicionais e explorar outras opções de configuração.</p>
<p>Agora você está pronto para aproveitar um prompt mais intuitivo e estilizado no seu PowerShell!</p>
